503
03:18:53,120 --> 03:19:13,488
So I think that's the best I can probably do with that. It's a little different what I was thinking but that's that's probably the direction to leave that in because those are the realities we face every day that quite frankly and with all due respect that this council doesn't have to deal with. And it is a tough job and it doesn't result in an easy day to day operations for us.

